        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:06:41 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:06:41 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lauren Sforza, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/20/july-4th-travel-expected-to-set-record.webp" alt="July 4th travel expected to set record"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">July 4th travel expected to set record</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The number of people traveling for the Fourth of July is expected to set a new record, according to projections from AAA.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/20/july-4th-travel-expected-to-set-record/"  >(Lauren Sforza, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:27:08 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:27:08 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Michael Bartiromo, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/20/donald-sutherland-celebrated-actor-from-mash-hunger-games-dies-at-88-son-kiefer-announces.webp" alt="Donald Sutherland, celebrated actor from 'M*A*S*H,' 'Hunger Games,' dies at 88, son Kiefer announces"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Donald Sutherland, celebrated actor from 'M*A*S*H,' 'Hunger Games,' dies at 88, son Kiefer announces</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Donald Sutherland, the prolific actor who starred in such films as “M*A*S*H,” “Ordinary People” and “The Hunger Games,” has died at the age of 88, son Kiefer Sutherland revealed Thursday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/20/donald-sutherland-celebrated-actor-from-mash-hunger-games-dies-at-88-son-kiefer-announces/"  >(Michael Bartiromo, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:39:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:39:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="ALFREDO PEÑA, Associated Press, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/20/alberto-seasons-first-named-tropical-storm-dumps-rain-on-texas-and-mexico-which-reports-3-deaths.webp" alt="Tropical Storm Alberto weakens over northeast Mexico after heavy rains killed 3"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tropical Storm Alberto weakens over northeast Mexico after heavy rains killed 3</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      TAMPICO, Mexico (AP) — Tropical Storm Alberto, the season’s first named storm, weakened Thursday as it moved inland over northeast Mexico after bringing heavy rains to parts of the parched region and leaving at least three dead.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/20/alberto-seasons-first-named-tropical-storm-dumps-rain-on-texas-and-mexico-which-reports-3-deaths/"  >(ALFREDO PEÑA, Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:24:54 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:24:54 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Christine Samra, KTLA 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/20/actor-donald-sutherland-dies-at-88.webp" alt="Actor Donald Sutherland dies at 88"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Actor Donald Sutherland dies at 88</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Actor Donald Sutherland has died at 88 years old. His son, actor Kiefer Sutherland, announced his father's passing in a post to X, formerly Twitter. "With a heavy heart, I tell you that my father, Donald Sutherland, has passed away," the post read alongside a photo of the father and son.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/20/actor-donald-sutherland-dies-at-88/"  >(Christine Samra, KTLA 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:08:41 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:08:41 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rich Johnson, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/21/water-pouring-vermont-state-rep-apologizes.webp" alt="Water-pouring Vermont representative apologizes to colleague"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Water-pouring Vermont representative apologizes to colleague</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rep. Jim Carroll set up a hidden camera and caught Mary Morrissey pouring water from a small plastic cup into his bag.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/21/water-pouring-vermont-state-rep-apologizes/"  >(Rich Johnson, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:23:15 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:23:15 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, PHL 17">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/21/an-agricultural-fire-spreads-through-settlements-in-southeast-turkey-leaving-at-least-5-dead.webp" alt="An agricultural fire spreads through settlements in southeast Turkey leaving at least 5 dead"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">An agricultural fire spreads through settlements in southeast Turkey leaving at least 5 dead</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      ANKARA, Turkey (AP) — Five people were killed and dozens more required medical treatment after a fire that started with the burning of crop stubble spread through settlements in southeast Turkey overnight, officials said Friday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/21/an-agricultural-fire-spreads-through-settlements-in-southeast-turkey-leaving-at-least-5-dead/"  >(Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 19:08:11 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 19:08:11 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Kaycee Sloan, KRON4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/20/cleveland-browns-player-arrested-for-dui-after-crashing-suv-into-florida-restaurant-police.webp" alt="Cleveland Browns player arrested for DUI after crashing SUV into Florida restaurant: police"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Cleveland Browns player arrested for DUI after crashing SUV into Florida restaurant: police</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Police said Phelps kept throwing his hands in the air and started rushing them to "do what [they] have to do." Without being instructed to do so, he turned around, put his hands behind his back and almost fell over.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/20/cleveland-browns-player-arrested-for-dui-after-crashing-suv-into-florida-restaurant-police/"  >(Kaycee Sloan, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
