  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/20/uk-investigating-second-tory-candidate-election-betting-allegations.webp" alt="UK investigating second Tory candidate over election betting allegations"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">UK investigating second Tory candidate over election betting allegations</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The U.K.&apos;s Gambling Commission is investigating a second Conservative public office candidate for allegedly placing a bet on the timing of the country&apos;s July 4 election.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/20/uk-investigating-second-tory-candidate-election-betting-allegations/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:23:18 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:23:18 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Joe Khalil, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/20/what-happens-us-russia-state-sponsor-terrorism.webp" alt="What happens if the US labels Russia a state sponsor of terrorism?"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">What happens if the US labels Russia a state sponsor of terrorism?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Russia, for the last few decades, has been united with the U.S. to oppose North Korea’s nuclear ambitions — until now.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/20/what-happens-us-russia-state-sponsor-terrorism/"  >(Joe Khalil, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 02:00:24 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 02:00:24 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/21/putins-ai-doctrine-seeks-semi-automated-military-moscow-could-look-china-help-expert-says.webp" alt="Putin's AI doctrine seeks semi-automated military as Moscow could look to China for help, expert says"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Putin's AI doctrine seeks semi-automated military as Moscow could look to China for help, expert says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Russia&apos;s urge to catch up to U.S. and China&apos;s AI dominance may cause it to take unnecessary risks, though current doctrine stresses the need to keep humans in the loop on decisions.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/21/putins-ai-doctrine-seeks-semi-automated-military-moscow-could-look-china-help-expert-says/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:17:23 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:17:23 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="KIM TONG-HYUNG and JIM HEINTZ, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/20/whats-known-and-not-known-about-the-partnership-agreement-signed-by-russia-and-north-korea.webp" alt="What's known, and not known, about the partnership agreement signed by Russia and North Korea"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">What's known, and not known, about the partnership agreement signed by Russia and North Korea</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SEOUL, South Korea (AP) — Both Russian President Vladimir Putin and North Korean leader Kim Jong Un say a new strategic partnership is a breakthrough, but what it means for their relationship is still uncertain.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/20/whats-known-and-not-known-about-the-partnership-agreement-signed-by-russia-and-north-korea/"  >(KIM TONG-HYUNG and JIM HEINTZ, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 16 Jun 2024 17:48:03 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 16 Jun 2024 17:48:03 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/16/german-police-shot-a-man-allegedly-threatening-them-with-an-ax-in-a-city-hosting-euro-2024-match.webp" alt="German police shot a man allegedly threatening them with a hammer in Euro 2024 host city Hamburg"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">German police shot a man allegedly threatening them with a hammer in Euro 2024 host city Hamburg</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BERLIN (AP) — German police said Sunday they shot and wounded a man who was threatening them with a pick hammer and a Molotov cocktail in the northern city of Hamburg, hours before it hosted a match in the European Championship soccer tournament.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/16/german-police-shot-a-man-allegedly-threatening-them-with-an-ax-in-a-city-hosting-euro-2024-match/"  >(Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:02:45 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:02:45 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lauren Irwin, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/21/biden-administration-russian-kaspersky-software-ban.webp" alt="Biden administration bans Kaspersky software over Russian ties"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden administration bans Kaspersky software over Russian ties</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Biden administration is issuing a total ban on the use of Kaspersky Lab’s software over its ties to Russia. The company’s software has been a concern of the U.S. government since at least 2017 because of the Russian government’s alleged influence over the software.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/21/biden-administration-russian-kaspersky-software-ban/"  >(Lauren Irwin, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 15 Jun 2024 20:17:23 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 15 Jun 2024 20:17:23 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JAMEY KEATEN and AAMER MADHANI, Associated Press, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/15/world-leaders-to-meet-at-swiss-resort-on-possible-ukraine-peace-roadmap-russia-is-notably-absent.webp" alt="World leaders meet in Switzerland to discuss a Ukraine peace roadmap. Russia is notably absent"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">World leaders meet in Switzerland to discuss a Ukraine peace roadmap. Russia is notably absent</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      OBBÜRGEN, Switzerland (AP) — Dozens of world leaders converged on a Swiss resort Saturday to discuss how to bring peace to war-ravaged Ukraine, though any hopes of a real breakthrough were muted by the absence of Russia.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/15/world-leaders-to-meet-at-swiss-resort-on-possible-ukraine-peace-roadmap-russia-is-notably-absent/"  >(JAMEY KEATEN and AAMER MADHANI, Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/tech/">Technology</a>
