    <h3 itemprop="headline">Source: Astros to recall outfielder Joey Loperfido</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Houston Astros are going to recall outfielder Joey Loperfido ahead of Friday’s game against the Baltimore Orioles. Loperfido becomes eligible for a recall Friday after spending ten days in Triple-A, after being optioned.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/21/source-astros-to-recall-outfielder-joey-loperfido/"  >(Ari Alexander, KPRC 2)</a>
