    <h3 itemprop="headline">Luke Whitlock delivers on Olympic dream by teaming up with Bobby Finke on U.S. distance swim team</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Finke, the defending Olympic champion in the event, finished in 7 minutes, 44.22 seconds. Whitlock was next at 7:45.19. He is the youngest American to make the team since Michael Phelps' breakthrough moment at age 15. And that's not all.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/19/luke-whitlock-delivers-on-olympic-dream-by-teaming-up-with-bobby-finke-on-u-s-distance-swim-team/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
