    <h3 itemprop="headline">Rep. Jamaal Bowman says Latimer is working for 'right-wing billionaires'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (PIX11) -- U.S. Rep. Jamaal Bowman and Westchester County Executive George Latimer, the two candidates in the Democratic primary for New York’s 16th Congressional District, faced off in a debate on PIX11 Tuesday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/19/rep-jamaal-bowman-says-latimer-is-working-for-right-wing-billionaires/"  >(Ben Mitchell, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
